<P>
Probably one of the most important votes on the June 5 ballot will be 
Proposition 119. 
</P>
<P>
A yes vote will stop the politicians from insulating themselves from the voters 
by drawing safe districts, will create a commission to draw fair boundaries for 
legislative districts, will give freedom-loving Californians an opportunity to 
vote out of office politicians with whom they disagree. 
</P>
<P>
Proposition 119 was written for the people for a change, not for the benefit of 
the politicians. For this reason you will find many politicians are working 
hard and putting a lot of money behind defeating it. 
</P>
<P>
It's time the voting public took control of our government. Let them know they 
are working for us. 
