<P>
Photo, Sockers' Rod Castro (17) tries to keep soccer ball a step ahead of Mark 
Karpun during first half Friday at San Diego Sports Arena. BRUCE K. HUFF / Los 
Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
