STUDENT EXPULSIONS; SCHOLARSHIPS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA051990-0076 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 221164 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 19, 1990, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
