<HEADLINE>
<P>
12 BRAZILIANS KILLED IN SOYBEAN PLANT BLAST 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
RIO DE JANEIRO 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A tank exploded at a soybean processing plant in southern Brazil, killing 12 
workers, the fire department said Friday. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
