<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Service Reports 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NBC Merges Production, Distribution Units: National Broadcasting Co. has merged 
its in-house production arm, NBC Productions, with its international program 
distribution unit, NBC International. The combination more typically reflects 
the structure of other production/distribution companies, said Executive Vice 
President John Agoglia, and would give each unit better access to the other's 
resources. NBC-P produces shows such as "Hardball," "Shannon's Deal" and 
"Mancuso, FBI." 
</P>
