<P>
TANSLEY WILL ATTEND CAL STATE FULLERTON 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Mike Tansley, a former Dana Hills High School track and cross-country athlete 
who attends Long Beach City College, has signed a national letter of intent to 
attend Cal State Fullerton. 
</P>
<P>
Tansley, who will have three years of eligibility to compete for the Titans' 
cross-country and track teams, finished fifth in the 1988 California state 
cross-country championships in his senior year at Dana Hills. 
